Application: VLAB-Monitoring 
Module: External-Scanner
Operation: VLAB_i::Gateway is {Observable, Trackable, Connectable}

Explanations: 
  Observable -> Ping-able from DynDns.org-Name to IP-address
  Trackable  -> IPGeolocation from IP-address to Country/ City/ Street
  Connectable -> Establish SSH-Connection & Execute a Demo "ls" command

Type: Python Native Application 

